sub_title: Looking for a job in Communications
summary:
Master in Strategic Communication from Lund University. For my bachelors I did Social Communication with emphasis in Communication, Education and Development; at Universidad de Cartagena.
I'm interested in creation of audiovisual content, PR and publicity.
I can highlight my creativity, good relation with others, punctuality, efficiency, and sense of belonging.
